                  <span class="text-md font-proximaNova font-semibold text-gray-600 group-hover:text-red-800">Summary: </span>
                  <ul class= "pl-4 list-disc marker:text-red-800">
                    <li class="text-md font-normal text-gray-600"> Develop and maintain the company's website and web applications. Work with the team to develop new features and improve the user experience.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-md font-proximaNova font-semibold text-gray-600 group-hover:text-red-800">Responsibilities: </span>
                  <ul class= "pl-4 list-disc marker:text-red-800">
                    <li class="text-md font-proximaNova text-gray-600"> Work togheter with the desing team to ensure the best user experience.</li>
                    <li class="text-md font-proximaNova text-gray-600"> Plan and develop the backoffice platform for the company, and the API for the mobile app.</li> 
                    <li class="text-md font-proximaNova text-gray-600"> Collaborate with the stakeholders to define the requirements and the scope of the projects.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="text-md font-proximaNova font-semibold text-gray-600 group-hover:text-red-800">Achivements: </span>
                  <ul class= "pl-4 list-disc marker:text-red-800">
